---
// ============================================================
// FOOTER — Sección de contacto + links finales
// Incluye: links a LinkedIn, GitHub, Email + copyright
// ============================================================
---

<footer id="contacto" class="py-20 border-t" style="border-color: #1e293b;">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">

    <!-- CTA de contacto -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 scroll-reveal">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #f8fafc;">
        Hablemos
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto" style="color: #94a3b8;">
        ¿Tienes un proyecto en mente o buscas un perfil técnico para tu equipo? Estaré encantado de conversar.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Links de contacto -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-16 scroll-reveal">

      <!-- Email -->
      <a
        href="mailto:contacto@bessondev.com"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl border font-medium text-sm transition-all duration-200"
        style="background-color: #0f172a; border-color: #1e293b; color: #cbd5e1;"
        onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='#334155'; this.style.color='#f8fafc'"
        onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='#1e293b'; this.style.color='#cbd5e1'"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/>
          <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
        </svg>
        Email
      </a>

      <!-- LinkedIn -->
      <a
        href="https://linkedin.com/in/bessondev"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl border font-medium text-sm transition-all duration-200"
        style="background-color: #0f172a; border-color: #1e293b; color: #cbd5e1;"
        onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='#3b82f6'; this.style.color='#3b82f6'"
        onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='#1e293b'; this.style.color='#cbd5e1'"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/>
          <rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"/>
          <circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/>
        </svg>
        LinkedIn
      </a>

      <!-- GitHub -->
      <a
        href="https://github.com/bessondev"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl border font-medium text-sm transition-all duration-200"
        style="background-color: #0f172a; border-color: #1e293b; color: #cbd5e1;"
        onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='#334155'; this.style.color='#f8fafc'"
        onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='#1e293b'; this.style.color='#cbd5e1'"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
          <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
        </svg>
        GitHub
      </a>

      <!-- CV -->
      <a
        href="/Harold_Besson_CV.pdf"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-medium text-sm transition-all duration-200"
        style="background-color: #3b82f6; color: #fff;"
        onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#60a5fa'"
        onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#3b82f6'"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"/>
          <polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/>
          <line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/>
        </svg>
        Descargar CV
      </a>

    </div>

    <!-- Línea divisora + copyright -->
    <div class="border-t pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-xs" style="border-color: #1e293b; color: #475569;">
      <p>© 2026 Harold Besson</p>
      <p class="font-mono">Ing. Sistemas · Puerto Ayacucho, Venezuela</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</footer>
